national united students for veterans health quick links stanford chapter site how to start a new chapter new chapter updates questions contact the webmaster welcome to national united students for veterans health the mission of united students for veterans health is to aid in the care and to enrich the lives of veterans across the nation ultimately we endeavor to bring our program to every va hospital in the nation that is in proximty to a university campus it is our cherished goal to foster relationships between patients and students in these relationships volunteers give back to those who gave so much we strive to create a world where students learn from the important life experiences of veterans and the veterans benefit from the youth and enthusiasm of the student volunteers find out more about the living memories project
